{
  "stem": "19690.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 65.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "My father went to Berlin to the biggest travel agency in Europe, which was [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Hansa, ?] and tried to get tickets to-- through-- on the Orient Express to go to Japan.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they said they had one ticket left and my father said, I will not go alone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "My mother insisted, go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We can come afterwards, but you get out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "He would not do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And this is part of that personality thing that I mentioned before that I criticize him for.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "It's the only thing I can criticize him for.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Anyway, he came back from Berlin without a ticket and there we sat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "In the meanwhile, on September 1st, early in the morning, big ruckus on the streets.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I might add I was just reading my diary that I wrote later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Three days before, a man from the government delivered to us ration cards with an open date.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And he told us at the time that he had those in his possession already since July of 1939.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "It is not something that Hitler wasn't planning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Anyway, on the 1st of September early in the morning, the ruckus on the streets was people driving away from the frontiers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "They evacuated everybody from the Western front, from the Siegfried line area.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And these people had little yellow rectangular signs on their cars.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "They had priority in everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "They were being put up in homes and the right direction was every home has to put up one family.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "So when we are offered a room, they [INAUDIBLE] the Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And-- but the schools were emptied and these people were living in the schools and they were living in any public building where they could put up cots.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
